Last week, I honored the winner of the inaugural Clash of Highway 29, the LaGrange College Panthers, on the floor of the U.S. House of Representatives.

Congratulations to the Panthers, led by Coach Wes Dodson, QB Henry Brodnax, WR Dami'on Thompson, and K Landon Eaker.

Wishing the Panthers the very best tomorrow against Centre College, and the rest of this season!

